COLUMBUS BAR ASSN.
v.
NYCE. 2017-1078 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 8, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On order to show cause. Kinsley Frampton Nyce, Attorney Registration No. 0003547, last known business address in Columbus, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to surrender certificate of admission and file an affidavit of compliance on or before February 2, 2018.
